# Network Diagnostic & Security Assistant

A comprehensive, AI-powered web application that provides professional-grade network diagnostics, performance optimization, and security assessment‚Äîall running directly in your browser with no server dependencies.

## üöÄ Key Features

### **Automatic Detection & Analysis**
- **Real-time Speed Testing**: Measures download/upload speeds, latency, and jitter using actual HTTP requests
- **Device Intelligence**: Auto-detects OS (Windows, macOS, iOS, Android), browser, and device type
- **Network Information**: Leverages browser APIs to detect connection type (WiFi, 4G, Ethernet) and effective connection quality
- **IP & Location Detection**: Identifies public IP, ISP, geographic location, and local network information via WebRTC
- **Security Scanning**: Simulates vulnerability detection for common router misconfigurations

### **Professional Diagnostics**
- **Wi-Fi Channel Optimization**: Interactive channel selector with congestion analysis for 2.4GHz, 5GHz, and 6GHz bands
- **Signal Strength Analysis**: Visual assessment with actionable placement recommendations
- **Usage-Based Optimization**: Tailored advice for gaming, video conferencing, 4K streaming, work-from-home, and office environments
- **Comprehensive Security Audit**: Evaluates router security posture, guest network setup, and connected device management

### **Advanced Capabilities**
- **Geolocation-Based Recommendations**: Suggests optimal DNS providers and CDN settings based on your location
- **Automatic Channel Recommendations**: Intelligently suggests best Wi-Fi channels based on interference patterns and device capabilities
- **Real-time Performance Monitoring**: Continuous testing with progress visualization and abort functionality
- **Professional Reporting**: Generates detailed health scores, issue summaries, and prioritized action checklists

## üéØ Technical Implementation

### **Browser APIs Utilized**
- **Network Information API**: Connection type, effective bandwidth, and RTT measurements
- **WebRTC**: Local IP address discovery without external dependencies
- **Geolocation & IP APIs**: Public IP and location data via ipify.org and ipapi.co
- **Fetch API**: Real speed testing with actual data transfers
- **Performance APIs**: Accurate timing measurements for latency calculations

### **Privacy & Security**
- **Zero Data Collection**: All processing happens locally in your browser
- **No External Storage**: Results are never saved or transmitted to servers
- **Ethical Design**: Focused on legitimate network optimization for networks you own or have permission to test
- **Transparent Operation**: Clear explanations of what each feature does and why

## üé® User Experience

### **Modern Interface**
- **Responsive Design**: Works seamlessly on desktop, tablet, and mobile devices
- **Gradient Color Scheme**: Professional aesthetic with clear visual hierarchy
- **Interactive Elements**: Animated progress bars, hover effects, and real-time updates
- **Intuitive Navigation**: Logical workflow from detection to analysis to recommendations

### **Professional Reporting**
- **Health Score System**: 0-100 scoring with color-coded severity indicators
- **Actionable Checklists**: Prioritized, step-by-step fixes with clear explanations
- **Technical Summaries**: Detailed metrics for IT professionals alongside simple explanations for non-technical users
- **Security Status Indicators**: Clear visualization of network security posture

