## ‚ö†Ô∏è Important Notes

- **Ethical Usage**: This tool is designed for legitimate network diagnostics on networks you own or have explicit permission to test
- **Browser Limitations**: Some advanced features may be limited by browser security restrictions
- **No Hacking Tools**: This application does not include penetration testing, port scanning, or any tools for unauthorized network access
- **Educational Purpose**: Designed to educate users about network performance and security best practices

## üí° Getting Started

Simply open the HTML file in any modern browser. The application will automatically begin detecting your network environment and provide real-time diagnostics without requiring any installation or configuration.

The interface guides you through comprehensive testing with clear results and actionable recommendations tailored to your specific network conditions and usage requirements.

